snippet.title: Mat Poochh Mere Mehboob | Kumar Sanu | Sadhana Sargam | Jackie Shroff | Hasti | 90's Romantic Song
snippet.description:
Enjoy the song "Mat Poochh Mere Mehboob" from the film Hasti features the beautiful vocals of Kumar Sanu, Sadhana Sargam, and Mukul Agarwal. This romantic duet is characterized by its melodious composition and heartfelt lyrics, capturing the emotions of love and longing. The Song is a lovely expression of romance, showcasing the talent of the artists and the timeless appeal of Bollywood music.

snippet.description:
#Vrusshabha #Mohanlal #VrusshabhaTrailer #RoarOfVrusshabha #VrusshabhaOn25thDecember #Nandakishore  
#EktaKapoor #SamarjitLanketsh #Raginidwivedi #Nayansarika #ConnekktMedia #BalajiTelefilms #AbishekSVyasStudios #AashirvadCinemas  #TSeriesSouth #TSeries #lalettan #SamCS #ResulPookutty #MalayalamFilm #TeluguFilm 

Presenting: The official Trailer of VRUSSHABHA - Malayalam 

Malayalam | Telugu | Hindi | Kannada

Vrusshabha is an epic that is high on storytelling. It explores the deep and unshakable bond between a father and son, a bond that faces an unexpected test. Spanning two worlds and timelines from the grandeur of a historic kingdom to the intensity of the modern era the film takes audiences on a powerful journey of love, sacrifice, and destiny.
 
Blending heart-stirring drama with breathtaking action, soul-stirring music, and stunning visuals, Vrusshabha is crafted to be an unforgettable big-screen experience. With Mohanlal portraying a king for the very first time in a bilingual epic, this film promises to leave a lasting impact long after the credits roll.

 Vrusshabha is a grand Pan Indian film shot simultaneously in Malayalam and Telugu, and dubbed in Hindi and Kannada.

Starring:Mohanlal, Samarjit Lankesh, Nayan Sarika, Ragini Dwivedi, Ajay, Neha Saxena, Vinay Varma, Garuda Ram, Ali, Kishore, Ayyappa P Sharma

snippet.description:
A film by Steven Spielberg. Disclosure Day is in theaters 06.12.26.

If you found out we werenâ€™t alone, if someone showed you, proved it to you, would that frighten you? This summer, the truth belongs to seven billion people. 
We are coming close to â€¦ Disclosure Day. 

Universal Pictures is proud to release a new original event film created and directed by Steven Spielberg. The film stars SAG winner and OscarÂ® nominee Emily Blunt (Oppenheimer, A Quiet Place), Emmy and Golden Globe winner Josh Oâ€™Connor (Challengers, The Crown), OscarÂ® winner Colin Firth (The Kingâ€™s Speech, Kingsman franchise), Eve Hewson (Bad Sisters, The Perfect Couple) and two-time OscarÂ® nominee Colman Domingo (Sing Sing, Rustin).
 
Based on a story by Spielberg, the screenplay is by David Koepp, whose previous work with Spielberg includes the scripts for Jurassic Park, The Lost World: Jurassic Park, War of the Worlds and Indiana Jones and the Kingdom of the Crystal Skull. Combined, those films earned more than $3 billion worldwide. Koepp also wrote the script for this 2025â€™s Jurassic World Rebirth. 

Disclosure Day is produced by five-time Academy AwardÂ® nominee Kristie Macosko Krieger (The Fabelmans, West Side Story) and by Spielberg for Amblin Entertainment. The executive producers are Adam Somner and Chris Brigham. 

Steven Spielberg is one of the industryâ€™s most successful and influential filmmakers. The top-grossing director of all time, Spielberg has helmed such blockbusters as Jaws, E.T. The Extra-Terrestrial, the Indiana Jones franchise and Jurassic Park. 
 
Among his myriad honors, he is a three-time Academy AwardÂ® winner, including OscarsÂ® for Best Director and Best Picture for Schindlerâ€™s List, which received a total of seven OscarsÂ®, and for Best Director for Saving Private Ryan. His most recent film, The Fabelmans, was released by Universal in 2022 and received seven Academy AwardÂ® nominations, including for Directing, Best Original Screenplay, Best Actress and Best Picture.

snippet.title: Aaja Hulchul Karenge | Kapil Sharma, Tridha | Afsana Khan | Kis Kisko Pyaar Karoon 2
snippet.description:
âœ¨ Aaja Hulchal Karenge â€“ Official Song | Kapil Sharma & Tridha Choudhury | Afsana Khan | Yug Bhusal | KKPK 2 | Ishtar Music

â€œAaja Hulchal Karengeâ€ is the latest energetic and romantic Hindi track from the upcoming movie Kis Kisko Pyaar Karoon 2, starring the charismatic Kapil Sharma and the stunning Tridha Choudhury. Filled with vibrant beats, fun chemistry, and youthful romance, this song brings a perfect mix of dance vibes and feel-good moments that make it an instant mood-booster.

snippet.title: Minecraft Speedrunner VS Hunter REVIVAL
snippet.description:
You asked for it. The path to 6 hunters begins. I need to prove that I have the skills and work my way up the Minecraft Manhunt ladder.

Follow my socials:
âž½ Twitter - @dream
âž½ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
âž½ Snapchat - @dream

George: @GeorgeNotFound   

We decided to call this series Minecraft Manhunt. This video is a different rendition of it, where there is ONE hunter, but I am NOT allowed to wear any armor. Not a single piece. 

This is a new Minecraft but, 1.21.10 challenge that we have decided to try. I try to beat the game, while my friend George tries to prevent me from doing it. It's a race, and it's super intense and we had a lot of laughs. I love doing these challenges.

Not Minecraft, But Water Rises or Minecraft, But Lava Rises, or any other but challenge like that. This is a speed run / speed runner of Minecraft against a killer / assassin

Music is from: @dreamproductionsXD 

#MinecraftManhunt
